videos.headline: Weber sheds tacklers on 23-yard TD run
videos.description: Mike Weber scores his second touchdown of the game, this one from 23 yards out, to extend Ohio State's lead over Northwestern to 17-7.

videos.headline: Northwestern overcomes 10-point deficit
videos.description: Northwestern QB Clayton Thorson hits Garrett Dickerson for a two-yard touchdown to tie the game with Ohio State at 17.

videos.headline: Samuel scores from three yards out for Ohio State
videos.description: Curtis Samuel takes the handoff and plows into the end zone to put Ohio State back out in front of Northwestern 24-17.

videos.headline: Barrett ends Wildcats' hopes with long third-down run
videos.description: Ohio State QB J.T. Barrett breaks loose for a 35-yard run on third down late in the fourth quarter, effectively ending Northwestern's bid for an upset.

videos.headline: Ohio State head coach Urban Meyer talks about his teams gritty performance in their 24-20 victory over Northwestern
